"UI: fix keyboard input so Escape and Enter no longer swallow text meant for "
"the search or history switch entries, and type-to-search works right after "
"startup"
msgstr ""

#: data/metainfo/org.gnome.GPaste.Ui.metainfo.xml.in:62
